/home/bshsqa/Shared/DALi_Doc_Generator/dali-guide_auto/cache/generation/final_candidates/image-loader.md:9:`Dali::Ui::AsyncImageLoader` loads image data asynchronously for dali-ui apps, while `Dali::Ui::ImageUrl` turns an encoded image buffer into a URL-style handle that can be passed through image-oriented code.
