/home/bshsqa/Shared/DALi_Doc_Generator/dali-guide_auto/cache/generation/final_candidates/image-loader.md:48:Each call to `Dali::Ui::AsyncImageLoader::Load` returns a `uint32_t` loading task id. Store that id when the result is still relevant to the current screen state. If the user navigates away, changes the requested image, or closes the image panel, cancel the stale request with `Dali::Ui::AsyncImageLoader::Cancel`.
