/home/bshsqa/Shared/DALi_Doc_Generator/dali-guide_auto/cache/generation/cli_raw/image-loader.stdout:115:`Dali::Ui::AsyncImageLoader::Cancel` is task-specific and returns whether that cancellation request was accepted. `Dali::Ui::AsyncImageLoader::CancelAll` is broader and is useful for screen teardown or replacing an entire result set.
